[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "I do not think that it is possible to combine several principles in the same government, so as at the same time to maintain freedom, and really to oppose them to one another.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "The form of government which is usually termed mixed has always appeared to me to be a mere chimera.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "The error arose from too much attention being paid to the actual struggle which was going on between the nobles and the people, without considering the probable issue of the contest, which was in reality the important point.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Unlimited power is in itself a bad and dangerous thing; human beings are not competent to exercise it with discretion, and God alone can be omnipotent, because His wisdom and His justice are always equal to His power.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "But no power upon earth is so worthy of honor for itself, or of reverential obedience to the rights which it represents, that I would consent to admit its uncontrolled and all predominant authority.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "In my opinion the main evil of the present democratic institutions of the United States does not arise, as is often asserted in Europe, from their weakness, but from their overpowering strength; and I am not so much alarmed at the excessive liberty which reigns in that country as at the very inadequate securities which exist against tyranny.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "I said one day to an inhabitant of Pennsylvania, \"Be so good as to explain to me how it happens that in a State founded by Quakers, and celebrated for its toleration, freed blacks are not allowed to exercise civil rights.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "\"You insult us,\" replied my informant, \"if you imagine that our legislators could have committed so gross an act of injustice and intolerance.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "\"Without the smallest doubt.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "\"How comes it, then, that at the polling booth this morning I did not perceive a single negro in the whole meeting?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "\"This is not the fault of the law: the negroes have an undisputed right of voting, but they voluntarily abstain from making their appearance.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "But in this case the majority entertains very strong prejudices against the blacks, and the magistrates are unable to protect them in the exercise of their legal privileges.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Tyranny usually employs arbitrary means, but, if necessary, it can rule without them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "In the United States the unbounded power of the majority, which is favorable to the legal despotism of the legislature, is likewise favorable to the arbitrary authority of the magistrate.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Power Exercised By The Majority In America Upon Opinion",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "In any constitutional state in Europe every sort of religious and political theory may be advocated and propagated abroad; for there is no country in Europe so subdued by any single authority as not to contain citizens who are ready to protect the man who raises his voice in the cause of truth from the consequences of his hardihood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "His political career is closed forever, since he has offended the only authority which is able to promote his success.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000027_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000027_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Every sort of compensation, even that of celebrity, is refused to him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Fetters and headsmen were the coarse instruments which tyranny formerly employed; but the civilization of our age has refined the arts of despotism which seemed, however, to have been sufficiently perfected before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000028_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000028_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Go in peace!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000028_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000028_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "I have given you your life, but it is an existence in comparably worse than death.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "The Inquisition has never been able to prevent a vast number of anti religious books from circulating in Spain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "The empire of the majority succeeds much better in the United States, since it actually removes the wish of publishing them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Unbelievers are to be met with in America, but, to say the truth, there is no public organ of infidelity. Attempts have been made by some governments to protect the morality of nations by prohibiting licentious books.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000031_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000031_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "In the United States no one is punished for this sort of works, but no one is induced to write them; not because all the citizens are immaculate in their manners, but because the majority of the community is decent and orderly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "In these cases the advantages derived from the exercise of this power are unquestionable, and I am simply discussing the nature of the power itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "This irresistible authority is a constant fact, and its judicious exercise is an accidental occurrence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "I am inclined to attribute the singular paucity of distinguished political characters to the ever increasing activity of the despotism of the majority in the United States.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "But the mass of the nation does not degrade itself by servitude: it often submits from weakness, from habit, or from ignorance, and sometimes from loyalty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000036_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000036_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "These peoples are miserable, but they are not degraded. There is a great difference between doing what one does not approve and feigning to approve what one does; the one is the necessary case of a weak person, the other befits the temper of a lackey.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "It seems, at first sight, as if all the minds of the Americans were formed upon one model, so accurately do they correspond in their manner of judging.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000039_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000039_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "They are very ready to communicate truths which are useless to you, but they continue to hold a different language in public.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "The Greatest Dangers Of The American Republics Proceed From The Unlimited Power Of The Majority",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "In the former case their power escapes from them; it is wrested from their grasp in the latter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000044_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000044_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "Anarchy is almost always produced by its tyranny or its mistakes, but not by its want of strength.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1444_133287_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1444/133287/1444_133287_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1444",
        "content": "It is important not to confound stability with force, or the greatness of a thing with its duration.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
